      "text": "C++ Comments",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "Comments can be used to explain C++ code, and to make it more readable. It can also be used to prevent execution when testing alternative code. Comments can be singled-lined or multi-lined.",
      "html": "<p>Comments can be used to explain C++ code, and to make it more readable. It can also be used to \nprevent execution when testing alternative code. Comments can be singled-lined or multi-lined.</p>"
    },
